{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A competitive puzzle-arcade fighting game where you stack colored blocks and detonate them using matching bombs. Chain together devastating combos and dominate the leaderboards! Play through an intense single-player campaign, challenge your friends online, and fight your way to the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stack blocks into clusters and clear them with bombs!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Match colors to build clusters, then detonate them with bombs of the same color to trigger explosive reactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2747930/extras/clip-sphere.gif?t=1740671009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Set up chains for even bigger combos!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place bombs strategically in advance to trigger chain reactions. The longer the chain, the higher your bonus\u2014and the stronger your attack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2747930/extras/cilp-chains.gif?t=1740671009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create connections across the board!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Link blocks of same color to the edges of the board. Each connected path adds to your score and your attack power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2747930/extras/cilp-line.gif?t=1740671009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unleash the powerful ring combo!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Surround one cluster with another to activate the ring effect\u2014each enclosed cluster boosts your score even further!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2747930/extras/cilp-ring.gif?t=1740671009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stack, link, and chain together the ultimate combos!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine chains, rings, and lines for maximum impact\u2014rack up insane points and overwhelm your opponents with crushing attacks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2747930?t=1740671009","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2747930?t=1740671009","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2747930/1ba4d00080d2022c3d2253cf5980dc4f68e3b8bd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740671009","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2747930/1ba4d00080d2022c3d2253cf5980dc4f68e3b8bd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740671009","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A competitive puzzle-arcade fighting game where you stack colored blocks and detonate them using matching bombs. Chain together devastating combos and dominate the leaderboards! Play through an intense single-player campaign, challenge your friends online, and fight your way to the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stack blocks into clusters and clear them with bombs!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Match colors to build clusters, then detonate them with bombs of the same color to trigger explosive reacti